PEOPLE of the STATE OF COLORADO v. VICTOR-AMERICAN FUEL COMPANY. No. 140. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit January 17, 1930. Robert E. Winbourn, Atty. Gen., for appellant. Frank E. Gove and Kenaz Huffman, both of Denver, Colo., for appellee.

Before LEWIS, Circuit Judge, and KENNEDY, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Dismissed January 17, 1930, on stipulation.
